# Everest Clarify

When multiple valid paths exist or credentials are missing:

1. Use `AskQuestion` with Russian labels and option «Другое / скажу голосом».
2. Accept free-text replies as «Другое».
3. Log decision in `docs/agents-log.md`.

Triggers: analytics choice, CDN host, Tilda block changes, WeChat QR, document section visibility.
